<br />

<br />
This camp is nearly impossbile without someone watchin that loc if you ask me, the range that the mobs path is rediculous and it would require incredible luck to actually find the spawn without someone standing there.
<br />

<br />
Also I personally think that if your tryin to find that PH watchin the level of the mob will do more harm then good, dont descriminate just highsun everything. Atleast that is my philosophy.</span></td>
